title: Jongens (Soundtrack van de Film)
description:
Hi guys

This is high-quality rendition of the soundtrack of the movie 'Jongens', a.k.a. Boys. (All 320kbps, except I Apologise)

Here's the tracklist:

1. I Apologise (Dear Simon) (by Moss)
2. Zomernamiddag (Summer Afternoon)
3. Na de kus (After the Kiss)
4. Trampoline
5. Training in de duinen (Training in the Dunes)
6. You Are My Sunshine (Marc's Serenade)
7. Zullen we hier voor altijd blijven? (Shall We Stay Here Forever?)
8. Midnight City (by M83)
9. Mislukte repetitie (Failed Rehearsal)
10. Zoektocht naar Eddy (Search for Eddy)
11. Gebroken hart (Broken Heart)
12. Laatste estafette (Last Relay Race)
13. Sieger komt tot het besef (Sieger Comes to the Realization)
